  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-8 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors scoped-out (acceptable at MRL 2). Operating envelope and applicability constraint are declared with concrete bounds; validation samples are sparse but coverage gaps are honestly documented.",
  "assuranceLevel": "Medium",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-centrifugal-pump-hemolysis-v3",
