      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry as the COU model. Operating points 1 and 2 are within the declared operating envelope (3.0 L/min at 2500 RPM; 5.0 L/min at 2800 RPM). Sparse coverage at envelope extremes is acknowledged; uncertainty uplift applied for extrapolated corners. Blood analogue (porcine blood) differs from human blood — documented as a known input uncertainty contributing to the combined UQ budget.",
