      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. Model setup, boundary condition assignment, and post-processing were performed by a single qualified analyst following a documented simulation plan reviewed by a second analyst. Peer review of simulation inputs and outputs is documented in the project quality record. Formal use-error FMEA is reserved for MRL 3 and above per project risk tiering."
